		{"id":"ds_stop_audit","type":"text","text":"🗄️ recording_compliance\n.stop_recording_audit\n← AuditStopRecordingConsumer","x":380,"y":100,"width":380,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"note_caveat","type":"text","text":"⚠️ **Honest caveat**\nNo direct caller of `restrictCallRecording` found inside the four consent packages. The wiring is event-mediated (`StopRecordingEvent` / `audit-stop-recording`) or lives outside those roots. Treat `RecordingSupervisorClient` as the **seam**, not a tight coupling.\n\n→ [[Subsystems/Consent/Use Cases/C - Enforce/C1 - Restrict Recording|UC-C1]]","x":380,"y":-60,"width":380,"height":200,"color":"4"}
	],
